& [InferenceJobResult] is outside preservation proposal
  + [focus] is reliability claim from worker
  + [inside] is two successful isolated runs on same prompt family
  + [boundary] is scope limited to that prompt family and run conditions
  + [outside] is uncertainty about generalization beyond tested cases
  + [inference] is model likely reliable for similar prompts under identical conditions
  + [caution] is avoid extrapolating to dissimilar prompts or environments
  + [next_step] is conduct additional tests across varied prompt families